# Upcoming Features - Q2 2024 Roadmap

As we continue to evolve Hex 21, we're excited to share our roadmap for Q2 2024. Here's what you can expect in the coming months.

## Planned Features

### 1. Advanced Search Capabilities
- Full-text search across all content types
- Filter by metadata, tags, and content type
- Search within mathematical equations

### 2. Collaborative Editing
- Real-time collaboration on documents
- Comment and review system
- Version comparison tools

### 3. Enhanced Export Options
- Custom PDF templates
- Interactive HTML exports
- EPUB support for e-readers

Stay tuned for these exciting updates! We'll be rolling them out gradually throughout Q2. 